<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>I'KNOW - Yapay Zeka Asistanƒ±</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #6366f1;
            --primary-hover: #4f46e5;
            --bg-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            --text-main: #1f2937;
            --text-muted: #6b7280;
            --card-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.15);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-gradient);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .layout-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            width: 95%;
            flex: 1;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1));
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .logo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        h1 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #6366f1, #a855f7);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .glass-card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
        }

        footer {
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-hover);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Forms & Inputs */
        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }

        textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
            background: #fff;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .checkbox-group {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* Result Specific */
        .result-meta {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .prompt-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .prompt-content {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .generated-markdown {
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .generated-markdown h1, .generated-markdown h2, .generated-markdown h3 {
            margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
        }

        .generated-markdown p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .generated-markdown code {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: 'ui-monospace', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .generated-markdown pre {
            background: #1e1e1e;
            color: #d4d4d4;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .generated-markdown pre code {
            background: none;
            padding: 0;
            color: inherit;
        }

        .alert-warning {
            background: #fff7ed;
            border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
            color: #9a3412;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        /* Main Layout Adjustment */
        .app-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            width: 95%;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 300px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0; /* Prevent overflow */
        }

        header {
            flex-basis: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Sidebar Styling */
        .history-card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            max-height: calc(100vh - 250px);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .history-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .history-list {
            list-style: none;
            overflow-y: auto;
            flex: 1;
            padding-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        .history-item {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .history-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-main);
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .history-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
            padding-left: 5px;
        }

        .history-time {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .clear-btn {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #ef4444;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .clear-btn:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* New Chat Button */
        .new-chat-btn {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .new-chat-btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .app-wrapper {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .sidebar {
                width: 100%;
                order: 2;
            }
            .main-content {
                order: 1;
            }
            .history-card {
                max-height: 400px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="app-wrapper">
        <header>
            <a href="/">
                <img src="/logo.png" alt="Yapay Zeka Logo" class="logo">
            </a>
            <h1>I'KNOW</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">En geli≈ümi≈ü Gemini modelleriyle g√º√ßlendirildi</p>
        </header>

        <aside class="sidebar">
            <a href="/" class="new-chat-btn">
                <span>‚ûï</span> Yeni Sohbet
            </a>
            
            <div class="history-card">
                <div class="history-title">
                    <span>üïí Ge√ßmi≈ü</span>
                    <% if session[:chat_history] && !session[:chat_history].empty? %>
                        <form action="/history/clear" method="post" style="display:inline;">
                            <button type="submit" class="clear-btn">Temizle</button>
                        </form>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
                <ul class="history-list">
                    <% if session[:chat_history] && !session[:chat_history].empty? %>
                        <% session[:chat_history].reverse.each do |chat| %>
                            <li class="history-item">
                                <div class="history-time"><%= chat[:timestamp] %></div>
                                <a href="/history/<%= chat[:id] %>" class="history-link" title="<%= chat[:prompt] %>">
                                    <%= chat[:prompt] %>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                        <% end %>
                    <% else %>
                        <li style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; padding: 1rem 0;">Hen√ºz ge√ßmi≈ü yok.</li>
                    <% end %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main class="main-content glass-card">
            <%= yield %>
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Created by <a href="https://github.com/garalo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">garalo</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
